 sequenceDiagram
 %% ===== Android (Google) Refund Flow =====
    participant Admin as Admin User
    participant  CommerceCoordinator(CC) as CC refund view
    participant GoogleAPI as Google Voided Purchases API
    participant CTEventBridge as EventBridge (CT Return created)

    Admin->>CommerceCoordinator(CC): GET /android/refunds
    CommerceCoordinator(CC)->>CommerceCoordinator(CC): Load refund config (e.g., last 3 days)
    CommerceCoordinator(CC)->>GoogleAPI: Request voided purchases (startTime)
    GoogleAPI-->>CommerceCoordinator(CC): Return list of voided purchases

    loop For each voided purchase
        CommerceCoordinator(CC)->>CommerceCoordinator(CC): Create refund object (ID, time)
        CommerceCoordinator(CC)->>CTEventBridge: Send refund signal (Android IAP)
    end

    CommerceCoordinator(CC)-->>Admin: Return success response (HTTP 200 OK)
